public void queue(BatchRequest batch,

           throws IOException
Queues the "get" request to the Shopping server into the given batch request.

Example usage:

           public void onSuccess(Product content, GoogleHeaders responseHeaders) {
             log("Success");
           }

           public void onFailure(GoogleJsonError e, GoogleHeaders responseHeaders) {
             log(e.getMessage());
           }
         });
